      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 66
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Immich app metrics come from its built-in OpenTelemetry exporter (`http_server_*`, `immich_*`). Its **Postgres** runs as a CloudNativePG cluster (`immich-db`) and **Valkey** is Immich's Redis-compatible cache \u2014 both in the `immich` namespace. CNPG/Valkey native metrics (`cnpg_*`/`pg_*`, `redis_*`) aren't scraped, so those sections show resource, disk-I/O and volume usage from cAdvisor + kubelet."
      }
